detector and a novel secondary attack detector designed based on 
unique TPS characteristics. With intact position data of trains, our 
detection system can effectively detect FDI attacks on trains{\rq} 
voltage and current measurements even if the attacker has full and 
accurate knowledge of the TPS, attack detection, and real-time system 
state. In particular, the GAD system features an adaptive mechanism 
that ensures low false-positive and negative rates in detecting the 
attacks under noisy system measurements. Extensive simulations driven 
by realistic running profiles of trains verify that a TPS setup is 
vulnerable to FDI attacks, but these attacks can be detected 
effectively by the proposed GAD while ensuring a low false-positive 
rate.},
